models

Class Screening

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.Screening

  • public class Screening
extends java.lang.Object
    The screening of the film. Contains the properties corresponding to the columns in the database for the screening. Has getter and setter functions to store data retrieved from the ScreeningDAO class.
